---
Syntax: spells

Lists all spells currently available to your character (spells with a mana
cost of 2 or more), along with their mana cost. The output is formatted in
three columns showing spell name and mana requirement.

Only spells your character can currently cast are listed -- spells you do
not have access to via class and level are excluded.

For all skills including non-mana skills, use LEARNED instead.
For a full class-by-class breakdown of available spells at each level,
use SLIST.

  spells    -- Shows usable spells and their mana costs.
  learned   -- Shows all usable skills/spells with proficiency.
  slist     -- Full spell/skill list by class and level.

See also: learned slist cast shelp
